## ?? What Was Wrong?
Visual Studio was **copying** your database file on every build, **erasing all your changes**.

## ? What's Fixed?
1. ? Connection string uses absolute path
2. ? Database file no longer copies to bin\Debug
3. ? All data saves to ONE location
4. ? Changes persist forever

---

